trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> class is the base class for request response classes, like the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse" /> and <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddResponse" /> classes.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> é a classe base das classes de resposta de solicitação, como as classes <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse" /> e <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddResponse" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.Controls" /> property contains an array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.Controls" /> também contém uma matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> retornada pelo servidor.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objetos retornados pelo servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.ErrorMessage" /> property contains the error message, if any, for this operation.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.ErrorMessage" /> contém a mensagem de erro, se houver, para esta operação.

trans-unit.source: The error message, if any, for this operation.
trans-unit.target: A mensagem de erro, se houver, para esta operação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.MatchedDN" /> property contains the matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.MatchedDN" /> contém o nome diferenciado correspondente retornado pelo servidor.

trans-unit.source: The matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: O nome distinto correspondente retornado pelo servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.Referral" /> property contains the server referrals.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.Referral" /> contém as referências de servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.RequestId" /> property contains the Request Identifier.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.RequestId" /> contém o identificador de solicitação.

trans-unit.source: User attempted to set the property value.
trans-unit.target: Um usuário tentou definir o valor da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.ResultCode" /> property contains the result code of the operation.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse.ResultCode" /> contém o código de resultado da operação.

trans-unit.source: The result code of the operation.
trans-unit.target: O código de resultado da operação.
